{"title":"You Think it Already Exists, But it Doesn’t: Introducing the First Chris King Seatpost Collar","link":"https://bikerumor.com/chris-king-seatpost-collar/","date":1729612800000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-front-on-th-Masi-jpeg.webp\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" alt=\"(Photo / Ron Frazelle)\" /></p>\n<p>I don’t know about you guys, but Chis King’s newly released Seatpost Collar came as a surprise to me. I seriously thought that <a href=\"https://chrisking.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Chris King Precision Components</a> already offered a seat collar. But, we all must have imagined it since this is their first. The new seat collar is a welcome addition that would sit pretty well between your Chis King Headset, Hubs, and Bottom Bracket.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-front-facing-from-the-top-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"852\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-front-facing-from-the-top-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Chris King Seatpost Collar front facing from the top\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-front-facing-from-the-top-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-front-facing-from-the-top-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-front-facing-from-the-top-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-front-facing-from-the-top-768x511.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-front-facing-from-the-top-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-front-facing-from-the-top-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photo / Chris King)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new Seatpost Collar looks to take a design nod from the iconic Chris King headset cups. As you’d expect, these new collars are precision-machined from aluminum. They are finished with the Chris King wood mark. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-Ck-Bee-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"852\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-Ck-Bee-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Chris King Seatpost Collar Ck Bee\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-Ck-Bee-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-Ck-Bee-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-Ck-Bee-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-Ck-Bee-768x511.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-Ck-Bee-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-Ck-Bee-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And, if you look closely, there is a lil’ “Chris King Buzz Bee” etched right there on the barrel nut. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-Midnight-closeup-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"852\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-Midnight-closeup-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Chris King Seatpost Collar Midnight closeup\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-Midnight-closeup-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-Midnight-closeup-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-Midnight-closeup-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-Midnight-closeup-768x511.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-Midnight-closeup-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-Midnight-closeup-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photo / Chris King)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-back-side-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-back-side-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Chris King Seatpost Collar back side\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-back-side-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-back-side-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-back-side-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-back-side-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-back-side-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-back-side-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photo / Ron Frazelle)</figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The barrel nut allows for the collar to keep optimal thread alignment while tightening the collar down. It also allows for even clamping force. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-red-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-red-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Chris King Seatpost Collar red\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-red-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-red-297x297.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-red-120x120.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-red-768x768.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-black-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-black-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Chris King Seatpost Collar black\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-black-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-black-297x297.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-black-120x120.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-black-768x768.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>The Chris King Seatpost Collar</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-mine-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-mine-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Chris King Seatpost Collar mine\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-mine-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-mine-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-mine-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-mine-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-mine-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-mine-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-stainless-hardware-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-stainless-hardware-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Chris King Seatpost Collar stainless hardware\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-stainless-hardware-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-stainless-hardware-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-stainless-hardware-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-stainless-hardware-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-stainless-hardware-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-stainless-hardware-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-weight-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-weight-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Chris King Seatpost Collar weight\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-weight-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-weight-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-weight-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-weight-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-weight-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-weight-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>I received my Chris King Seatpost Collar in Matte Turquoise in the 34.9 size. And It’s as beautiful as you’d expect any product from Chris King to be. It weighed in at a respectable 32 grams with stainless steel hardware. Not the lightest, but it’s also pleasantly robust in its construction. So, there is a give and take here.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-lip-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-lip-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Chris King Seatpost Collar lip\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-lip-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-lip-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-lip-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-lip-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-lip-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-lip-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-backside-top-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-backside-top-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Chris King Seatpost Collar backside top\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-backside-top-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-backside-top-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-backside-top-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-backside-top-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-backside-top-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-backside-top-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It has a pronounced lip that keeps it sitting pretty on the top of your seat tube, like most seat collars. Mine looks great on the Masi Incanto Ti, where I have a matching Chris King headset installed. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-front-on-th-Masi-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-front-on-th-Masi-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Chris King Seatpost Collar front on th Masi\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-front-on-th-Masi-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-front-on-th-Masi-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-front-on-th-Masi-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-front-on-th-Masi-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-front-on-th-Masi-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-front-on-th-Masi-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photo / Ron Frazelle)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>My Thoughts</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Go get one. I think the Chis King Seatpost Collar is not only something most of us thought already existed but, something you should probably own. It’s a high-quality, reasonably priced, USA-made product that will last the life of your bicycle and likely longer. It doesn’t get more simple and elegant.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>The Seatpost Clamp Retail &amp; Detail </h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-colors-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"448\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-colors-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Chris King Seatpost Collar colors\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-colors-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-colors-297x104.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-colors-120x42.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Chris-King-Seatpost-Collar-colors-768x269.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $48 ($56 for the two-tone Black/Gold)</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Available in four sizes: 30.0, 31.8, 34.9 (tested), and 36.4</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Clamp Material: Aluminum</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Bolt: Stainless Steel</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Barrel Nut: Stainless Steel</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Torque Spec: 6Nm (max)</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Put some additional color pop on your bike and go get yours now by hitting the link below:</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://chrisking.com/\" target=\"_blank\">ChrisKing.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/chris-king-seatpost-collar/\">You Think it Already Exists, But it Doesn’t: Introducing the First Chris King Seatpost Collar</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"ed39a7b7b3f4eeb7ef271a8a9d10f54a98a0bf3168fc8c41925f906a5d0a165b","category":"Cycling"}